latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It wouldn’t be La Mer without Miracle BrothTM. Designed with peeling power to free skin from dullness while clarifying pores,
The Micro Peel is also infused with Miracle BrothTM and Miracle Broth Oils to nourish skin in tandem so skin emerges more hydrated and refined.
There’s always time to refine your regimen. Incorporate The NEW Micro Peel to shake up your nightly routine for visibly refined skin by morning.

The AHA (and BHA, PHA) factor. Crafted with a blend of poly-acids to exfoliate, retexturize and help clear impurities, our new concentrated powerhouse, The Refining Ferment, smoothes, stimulates renewal and strengthens skin for a radiant transformation by morning.

The NEW Micro Peel shakes up the definition of an overnight peel and what it can do. To fully reap its refining benefits, gently shake to mix and activate the bi-phase formula so doses of peeling acids blend with restorative oils to help replenish skin while resurfacing.
Give skin a fresh start with the refining power of The NEW Micro Peel and nourish it with the replenishing benefits of Miracle BrothTM and Miracle Broth Oils.
Discover the beauty beneath with our new “facial-in-a-bottle.” Introducing The Micro Peel, La Mer’s newest overnight treatment to refine, replenish and rebuild.
Micro drops, macro skin refinement. Reveal the beauty beneath with the latest innovation from La Mer.

Strength from the sea. Our potent Concentrated Miracle Broth™ taps into the self-regenerating power of Giant Sea Kelp to help reduce the appearance of visible signs of inflammation — just one of the ways The Concentrate helps prevent signs of premature aging.

Jet. Set. Protect. The Concentrate makes for the perfect travel mate. Whether your destination is 
sun-soaked or snow-covered, our most potent barrier-strengthening serum staves off signs of environmental stress and keeps skin soothed in its own mini-sanctuary of rest and repair. Where will The Concentrate take you?

Let’s have a closer at the Concentrated Miracle Broth™-infused treatments everyone’s talking about.

The Concentrate is our richest serum with the barrier-strengthening power to keep skin stable, soothed and protected from irritants like pollution and microdust. It can even speed up skin’s barrier recovery when used before and after certain dermatologic treatments, like a peel or laser.

The Eye Concentrate is our most adored eye cream that will have fine lines, wrinkles and dark circles fading from view. A proprietary antioxidant blend helps neutralize free radicals to prevent 
future damage.

The Neck and Décolleté Concentrate is an entire ritual unto itself in one glossy little jar. The feather-soft brush applicator follows the neckline and collarbones perfectly – it’s a mini-spa moment to make your most alluring area look more lifted look and feel firmer.

Stressed from the workday? Sun-exposed from the weekend? Your skin feels the effects just like you do. Come back to center with The Concentrate – our strengthening serum designed to empower skin’s defenses and soothe away stress. An indulgence we love to love.

Improved barrier strength isn’t the only thing that’s essential to efficacious skincare. In addition to our barrier-boosting serum salve The Concentrate, we recommend experiencing all that La Mer has to offer in the form of our personalized Essentials regimen. Select your eye treatment, serum and moisturizer for the full range of La Mer’s renewing power.

latestPosts.caption:
This Pride Month, discover the artistic world of @deveryjacobs. We asked the actor and filmmaker how she stays energized to forge new creative paths and tell inspired stories.

“Daydreaming is really important. I associate connecting to my artistic practice with creating magic — there is an element of magic that happens where all of a sudden, you’ll be hit with inspiration that floods into you. There will be entire worlds and characters and stories created, and you’re conjuring that out of nothing.”

Meet some of the LGBTQIA+ creatives currently inspiring Devery: @giiwedinindizhinikaaz @kararoselles @shesanargonaut. 

Tarot cards by @ricardocavolo.

#LGBTQIA #Pride

What gets @deveryjacobs brimming and buzzing with inspiration? In celebration of Pride Month, the actor shares a glimpse into her creative process and how she works to embody the essence of new characters.

“With each role I take on, it needs to touch on some inner truth, whether that’s finding the physicality, whether that’s learning what secret the character is holding onto. That’s the space that I try and create from.”

Tarot cards by @ricardocavolo.
#LGBTQIA #Pride

“The celebration of Pride is a reminder to really relish in the stories I’m creating for myself but also for my community,” says actor, advocate, filmmaker, and writer @deveryjacobs. 

“Connecting to my queerness is also connecting to my culture as an Indigenous person. There are so many more stories from our communities that are still left to be told.”

Embody your essence. Embrace your energy. Come back soon for more from Devery as we celebrate Pride Month.

Tarot cards by @ricardocavolo.

#LGBTQIA #Pride
